Currency Converter (CLI)
Description:
This is a Python-based Currency Converter that allows users to convert an amount from one currency to another using hardcoded exchange rates (for demo purposes).
It supports multiple currency conversions like USD to INR, EUR to USD, etc.
How It Works:
The user is asked to input:
The source currency
The target currency
The amount to convert
The app uses a dictionary of exchange rates to perform conversion.

